{"tid":1757271,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA 20 Ultimate Team 討論區 (91) 祈求民主與自由 萬世都不朽","createTime":"2019-11-26T12:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T06:50:53.000Z","uid":253445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9e01594826996be9557b575bd7348c4d51296d52","tid":1757271,"uid":253445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FckjBrs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFckjBrs.gif&h=bb509340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入FIFA20 Ultimate Team討論區<br />\n<br />\n開始前請先睇Q&amp;A，睇完搵唔到你想知嘅野先問，好多你想知嘅野都係第一版！拜託曬！<br />\n<br />\nFIFA UT web app: <a href=\"https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.easports.com%2Ffifa%2Fultimate-team%2Fweb-app&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx97vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=abe1f7a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app</a><br />\n<br />\n球員資料database:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://futbin.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffutbin.com&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx97vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=a01baaba\" target=\"_blank\">http://futbin.com</a><br />\n<br />\nSBC 答案 (參考idea, 抄足貴到仆街)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36xts7Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36xts7Q&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx97vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=bd732f3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36xts7Q</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n1.係咪有金包送架?<br />\n答:今年自動送pack，唔使入code<br />\n<br />\n2. 點賺錢?<br />\n答:踏實d, 打比賽, 要快手就去淘寶課金, 但EA話會嚴打買賣coins, 後果自負<br />\n玩耐左可以試下炒卡。<br />\n留意賣卡會收「稅」，成功交易會抽5%，如賣10,000 coins成交，實收9,500<br />\n<br />\n3. 咩係chemistry?<br />\n答:簡單d黎講, 高chemistry d隊員走位好d唔會成碌木咁唔走位, 另外個人chemistry會影響能力<br />\n<br />\n4. 咁點加chemistry呀?<br />\n答:位置、球員之間嘅連線、教練、loyalty等等都會影響chemistry。<br />\n<br />\n5. 咩係綠色連線?<br />\n答:球員同球員之間ge連線:國籍,聯賽,球隊<br />\n符合兩樣就夠有綠色連線<br />\n<br />\n6. 咩係IF?咩係TOTW?點解有d卡會係黑色?<br />\n答:每星期三晚都會有新嘅TOTW (team of the week)<br />\n出嘅人會有張加強版嘅黑色卡，又叫IF (in form)<br />\n<br />\n7.chemistry style係咩黎?持續幾耐?<br />\n答: 唔同chemistry style會對球員某d 能力有唔同提升, 每個球員一開始都有basic呢個style<br />\n你會見到每項能力都有一格V形箭嘴, chemistry style卡係永遠套用於某個球員, 直至你apply另一張落去<br />\n<br />\n8: 你地成日講H/H, H/M, M/L 係乜勁呀?<br />\n答: 代表球員work rate, H-high, M-medium, L-low<br />\n<br />\n9: 乜野係ONE TO WATCH呢？<br />\n答: 就係呢個球員今季先轉會，咁就有幸比FIFA觀察<br />\notw卡 係會跟inform卡 upgrade數值，卡面都會跟埋IF<br />\n<br />\n10:我DR SB 幾分幾分夠唔夠KEEP RANK 1?<br />\n答:<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2oMWQ9m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oMWQ9m&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx97vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=b8a8bae1\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2oMWQ9m</a><br />\n<br />\n11:點樣開新po？<br />\n答: 去#1右上角三點，禁以此內容開新主題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMetqpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMetqpP.png&h=603a033d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12:今年點睇walkout?<br />\n答: walkout 上面兩個橙光會不同步地閃，有board嘅就同步<br />\n<br />\n13:頭5場WL 有咩用? 究竟WL 係點配對手俾我? <br />\n頭5場對手係random但決定你的起手ranking<br />\n贏曬即係+5 赢3場即係+1+1+1-1-1 &gt; +1 已經有極大既分別<br />\n但EA亦承認因為好難做到prefect matching,個system係容許0-5既所謂誤差<br />\n所以假設你現在就算係+1 係唔太好彩既情況下 你係有機會遇到+6既對手 反之亦然<br />\n<br />\n14: 對手球會/陣容名損害我哋七百萬人嘅心靈，可以點做？<br />\n答: 唔檢舉唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Nb400w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Nb400w&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx97vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=c64198e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Nb400w</a>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g00mYmG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg00mYmG.png&h=825699be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n15:點解我要用不推文回覆？<br />\n答:你想唔想中walkout? 打機呢啲唔重要嘅po就唔好阻到正經嘢上熱門啦(詳閱：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1660096\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1660096</a>）<br />\n<br />\n16:咩叫肥料卡？<br />\n答:肥料就係作用解SBC、靚國藉靚聯賽、高rate低能嘅人,EG. Carvajal , Pique, Rakitic<br />\n<br />\n17:咩叫META卡？<br />\n答:實用普金人 / 特別卡,例子: 84 Walker , 82 Semedo , 81 Ssk , 80 Mendy。META卡係唔受總分所限 , 玩家覺得勁嘅卡<br />\n<br />\n18:藍卡，RTTF又係啲乜？<br />\n答: 藍卡 = UCL 卡 , 有得打歐冠先有嘅卡/RTTF = ROAD TO THE FINAL, 踢緊歐聯嘅球員 , 佢每晉一級就會升一分總分<br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/3735GB0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3735GB0&h=ed0af756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n派獎時間<br />\nSB：MON 8AM<br />\nDR：THURS 3PM<br />\nWL：THURS 4PM<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVA9s5U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVA9s5U.png&h=c48531bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBppBac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLBppBac.gif&h=dfaa4189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我愛EA！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJ7nFg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJ7nFg0.jpg&h=5df15dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nICON SWAPS 1<br />\n由即日起自十二月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgGLpYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgGLpYA.jpg&h=cc9c9c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1:點為之第一手擁有球員？<br />\n答: 抽、租借、做SBC、Objective得返嚟嘅都算係<br />\n<br />\n2:IF, OTW, Champions呢啲算唔算黃金球員？<br />\n答: 算，你去Club search filter黃金嘅都算金人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>另外，請善用不推文回覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔用不推文回覆者一世無walkout<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"37f1f34eaf925f932d600333190ef177746a5da1","tid":1757271,"